metadata.description:
As water reflects the face, so oneâ€™s life reflects the heart. - Proverbs 27:19.

God's creation always amazes us, when we come across his artistic touch behind every creation on this Earth. He has a plans for humans and fellow beings. 

He gave us nature, to nurture us and to get refreshed whenever we are in stress.  Just embrace the nature and it just heals you from inner.

This is a landscape of "Pamuleru Lake" near "Maredumilli", located in state of Andhra Pradesh, India.
